# AdGuard Home — recursive DNS + ad/tracker filtering + split-horizon for
# loogi.ch and example.com.
#
# This stack is APIRATIONAL today. Currently airbase forwards to upstream
# DNS directly; AdGuard is here so the move to a self-hosted resolver is a
# `docker compose up -d` away on whichever host gets nominated.
#
# Configuration (admin password, upstream resolvers, blocklists,
# split-horizon rewrites) lives in ./conf/AdGuardHome.yaml after the
# first-run setup wizard. Nothing needs to be parameterised at compose time.
